<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>They've fallen head over heels for each other.</p>

<p>And on Wednesday, Machine Gun Kelly gushed about how in love he is with new flame Megan Fox.</p>

<p>'I didn't know what [love] was until me and her made eye contact... That's when I was like, 'Whoa!'' the rapper, 30, revealed during an interview on The Howard Stern Show, as reported by People.</p>

<p>Love at first sight: Machine Gun Kelly gushed about new flame Megan Fox on Wednesday, telling Howard Stern: ''I didn't know what [love] was until me and her made eye contact... That's when I was like, 'Whoa!''</p>

<p>The Houston native, born Colson Baker, added: 'That was my first experience with being open to love and stuff like that. I definitely wasn't set up to believe that that's something that could ever exist.'</p>

<p>MGK and Transformers star Fox, 34, went public with their romance in May after meeting on the set of the movie Midnight In The Switchgrass.</p>

<p>Filming on the production was taking place in Puerto Rico when it was halted due to the COVID-19 pandemic.  </p>

<p>Kelly told Stern that it had been 'love at first sight' when they met. </p>

<p>Head over heels: The rapper added: 'That was my first experience with being open to love and stuff like that. I definitely wasn't set up to believe that that's something that could ever exist'</p>

<p>Passion: MGK and Transformers star Fox, 34, went public with their romance in May after meeting on the set of the movie Midnight In The Switchgrass </p>

<p>Together: Fox appeared as a crazy girlfriend in the music video for Kelly's single Bloody Valentine from his fifth studio album Tickets to My Downfall, which drops on Friday</p>

<p>The couple made things Instagram official with a black-and-white mirror selfie and Kelly posted it with the caption: 'Waited for eternity to find you again ...'</p>

<p>Fox took to her own Instagram, writing: 'Achingly Beautiful Boy... My heart is yours.</p>

<p>She later appeared as a crazy girlfriend in the music video for the rapper's single Bloody Valentine from his upcoming fifth studio album Tickets to My Downfall, which drops on Friday.</p>

<p>The actress is estranged from her husband Brian Austin Green with whom she shares sons Noah, who turns eight on Sunday, Bodhi, six, and Journey, four,</p>

<p>Fox and Beverly Hills, 90210 alum Green had started dating after meeting on the set of a TV sitcom in 2004. Following an on-off-on again engagement, the pair tied the knot in 2010.</p>

<p>Split: The actress is estranged from her husband Brian Austin Green whom she met on the set of a TV sitcom in 2004 and married in 2010 (pictured last December)</p>

<p>Family: The estranged couple have three sons together - Noah, who turns eight on Sunday, Bodhi, six, and Journey, four</p>
